T1  - The signaling value of legal form in entrepreneurial debt financing
AU  - Bracht, Felix
AU  - Mahieu, Jeroen
AU  - Vanhaverbeke, Steven
JO  - Journal of Business Venturing
VL  - 39
IS  - 3
